{"type":"message","id":"0c238b26","parentId":"064bb6dc","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:18:10.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Assessing cron event handling**\n\nI’m thinking about whether to append a log for the cron event. Maybe that’s unnecessary. It seems straightforward to return nothing or simply indicate that everything is good. Since this is in chat, I could use a concise message like \"WATCHDOG_CHECK: 正常，无需处理。\" This keeps things clear and to the point. It's important to balance clarity with brevity, so I’m keeping that in mind as I decide!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_012f2ac522dad4fc0169c2c74f1dbc8191ae47565fdafee44b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwsdSrbWPd457LaH5tEJlfURX5oKAYR-rZw0MWOqlFOy4GEAvoUvH2SN46Xow_JgDdKZwrx7bkrVfX_bflwPQc5APDBZ9N879EYUaOfag9AtCgTS9Dyq3uTFaDBluvWDyUm9hbADEZi0fHbIBYHkjd_4BF6pJZxY5VuiD_uUk2yrVYBuVUj49iPRXG4EThtYqP6ip-3BjhFRbnFG86EizWxlkuGoPxjZm7xTAxLQMHE1zLvJxViiAMg8X4PwhBqgcoJToDKS3L5moxtmec_Ez44mbn5IXWKG-0qXOed-K1F1zrGSSIvpdD0KIiTmlM2M2plIqjV4ZkyvEohxPH52yHHbtHbQPRoBVXOLVf1BzDmSMPbx-ZcLjfvd50BgJeeqKsBvI2qo9935Eijbmrrd-Qkm380ODqg8DnpWgO2lCnpnC9Uotc-I6mKBwinEg32qYd9i_fXbQFASBmyl4_jiNJKKVLm_WNUFX9UFjvx2UAPM0pVhzHvMnSOUolJBqMpMHvqEpJrItripQmKOoNNeuLTyWIxpmVFC5Yx25bIupkbUch3bjoW2Pfp9VaQElSTOVYlCby5--a_nCVOC35cuNbDTajNWLUhJbEma-tM75UyFrZpfDGZwpPUrNPBFPLQ5W8_YMzZDMo7jYY5dnEocvmbcry0eaVTzstz_FgMK6PC2ut03PG6XMUOkwEl-6SjOUp45ELOP-_wBjGbQSr-D5T4ZOqrl3XMbz8e-jWeuZ7by7O65zzVtE0R1GhWi3c6EhdW2mk-E7N5Xf0v2ZrkLHwRGkUm8sZNhxrkwW2mP2s-Wi2LDWUjU4t46hH57vxonaM4YKXsXBnxO2xQbPRjGLD8ComooOWcZDkFm0RIaJxRHJ9VCgUAe9E8LQbOqduAjQ2jZQqHetL29UaVqHEFeYWfFyWK9_4jOvoe7txhomjc4mt9JFrF0OSwV8heX7FbO9f86hduqRBRf03hXah1fMKsfirMiZF6nJEFjwIBH_OxxYDex4rmom-F_FlNI142uUcyEIUPD8Hi0bKa5ZVqpNH39xk0czRnEDRb9wlaXc4xV0ejE=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Assessing cron event handling**\\n\\nI’m thinking about whether to append a log for the cron event. Maybe that’s unnecessary. It seems straightforward to return nothing or simply indicate that everything is good. Since this is in chat, I could use a concise message like \\\"WATCHDOG_CHECK: 正常，无需处理。\\\" This keeps things clear and to the point. It's important to balance clarity with brevity, so I’m keeping that in mind as I decide!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"watchdog 正常。\n\n- gateway service: running\n- RPC probe: ok\n- `GET /healthz`: `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`\n\n按你的偏好，正常情况不打扰、不告警。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_012f2ac522dad4fc0169c2c7521c2c8191b5c2a67bd0e4a334\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":793,"output":101,"cacheRead":15872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16766,"cost":{"input":0.0019825000000000003,"output":0.001515,"cacheRead":0.003968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007465500000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774372685806,"responseId":"resp_012f2ac522dad4fc0169c2c74e32e88191829f0d88f685e3ab"}}
